Also we enjoin upon you that you do cause to be celebrated continually‚ according to the ordinance made touching that matter, the mass of the blessed and glorious Virgin‚ to the daily celebration whereof in the parish church of Kirby aforesaid you recognise yourselves and the said your priory to be bound under strict obligation.⁴
